name: TurboTax 2012 Tax Return File
summary: Learn about .TAX12 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: NOTE: While TAX12 files can be opened with TurboTax, most TurboTax 2012 tax returns are saved with a .TAX2012 file extension.

description: Tax return created with TurboTax 2012 tax preparation software; contains United States tax forms for the 2012 tax year along with data entered by the user; may be encrypted, which requires a password to open.
